author: Adam Savage’s Tested
description:
Why didn't MythBusters use professionals (vs. Padawan "rejects") for the Star Wars High Ground myth? Does Adam regret the Killer Cable Snap findings? Why did the giant Newton's cradle fail, and where did the flamethrowers go after Fire vs. Ice was filmed? In this live stream excerpt Adam answers these questions from Tested members @leatherelf2078, @YT-TheLegacy, @cyberpunkmodsdotcom and @SuperAngus52, whom we thank for their support. Is there a myth you feel the MythBusters got wrong?

0:00 Star Wars
2:29 Killer Cable Snap
10:49 Newton's Cradle
11:32 Fire vs Ice
The Thing Adam Refused to Do When Asked by a MythBusters Producer: https://youtu.be/y6qLhY423OE
